386
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:48,400
What should we do?

387
00:23:03,350 --> 00:23:05,440
Now that I suddenly have some free time,

388
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:06,700
I don't know what to do.

389
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:09,800
How about playing chess?

390
00:23:11,310 --> 00:23:12,770
That's boring.

391
00:23:14,400 --> 00:23:16,530
Why don't we play something exciting?

392
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:22,580
Put me down!

393
00:23:22,660 --> 00:23:24,460
Zhang Hailou, put me down!

394
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:26,900
Put me down!

395
00:23:26,920 --> 00:23:28,000
I won't!

396
00:23:28,970 --> 00:23:30,180
Sit tight, Shrimpie!

397
00:23:31,610 --> 00:23:32,050
Stop!

398
00:23:32,070 --> 00:23:32,730
Turn right!

399
00:23:34,940 --> 00:23:35,730
Shrimpie,

400
00:23:36,090 --> 00:23:37,690
the weather is finally fine.

401
00:23:37,700 --> 00:23:38,550
Let's go sea fishing.

402
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:40,080
You call this fine weather?

403
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:41,700
I can't go.

404
00:23:42,240 --> 00:23:43,480
Isn't the boat right there?

405
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:44,540
Just bring it over.

406
00:23:44,810 --> 00:23:45,770
The sea is too rough.

407
00:23:45,770 --> 00:23:47,110
We can't go out to sea.

408
00:23:47,270 --> 00:23:48,500
I'll pay you more.

409
00:23:49,090 --> 00:23:50,570
It's not about money.

410
00:23:51,010 --> 00:23:52,230
Why can't we go?

411
00:23:52,850 --> 00:23:54,240
The sea is too rough.

412
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:56,770
-I'll double it, okay?
-Still dreaming things can be like they used to be?

413
00:23:56,770 --> 00:23:58,360
Why can't I make you understand?

414
00:23:58,360 --> 00:23:59,740
These waves aren't dangerous at all.

415
00:23:59,740 --> 00:24:01,940
You're just a burden now.

416
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:02,940
Figure it out yourself.

417
00:24:02,940 --> 00:24:04,620
Why can't I reason with you?

418
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:06,240
If you want to go so badly,

419
00:24:06,240 --> 00:24:08,100
find someone else to take you. Go.

420
00:24:08,810 --> 00:24:11,300
Trash shouldn't be alive.

421
00:24:11,550 --> 00:24:12,540
Like I care!

422
00:24:14,350 --> 00:24:15,310
Don't hold me up.
I need to haul in the net and go home.

423
00:24:15,310 --> 00:24:16,640
Stop fooling yourself.

424
00:24:25,670 --> 00:24:26,930
[Excessive use of strychnine may lead to madness;
physicians should prescribe with utmost caution.]

425
00:24:27,040 --> 00:24:29,180
[Long-term use
may lead to personality changes.]

426
00:24:30,470 --> 00:24:32,070
What is wrong with me lately?

427
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:32,470
[Long-term use
may lead to personality changes.]

428
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:34,490
[Pharmacy]

429
00:24:36,580 --> 00:24:37,420
[Pharmacy]

430
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:43,410
Mr. Zhang,

431
00:24:43,590 --> 00:24:45,810
there is nothing wrong with your health.

432
00:24:45,810 --> 00:24:47,550
You can stay under observation
for a while.

433
00:24:47,550 --> 00:24:49,480
Come to me if you have any problems.

434
00:26:17,790 --> 00:26:18,400
