437
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:57,040
Mimi, come down!

438
00:27:08,270 --> 00:27:09,240
Come down.

439
00:27:09,810 --> 00:27:10,440
Come down.

440
00:27:14,320 --> 00:27:14,990
Let me do it.

441
00:27:18,510 --> 00:27:19,510
Can you?

442
00:27:37,700 --> 00:27:39,350
Who told you
to throw the stone at the cat?

443
00:27:39,350 --> 00:27:40,850
You almost killed it!

444
00:27:40,900 --> 00:27:41,830
-Yuanbao!
-I...

445
00:27:41,850 --> 00:27:42,530
Come down!

446
00:27:42,770 --> 00:27:43,570
Come down!

447
00:27:43,850 --> 00:27:44,590
Are you okay?

448
00:27:46,310 --> 00:27:47,370
What are you doing?

449
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:49,510
I was just trying to help.

450
00:27:49,510 --> 00:27:50,160
Mother,

451
00:27:50,270 --> 00:27:51,770
he threw a stone at Mimi!

452
00:27:51,850 --> 00:27:52,310
I...

453
00:27:52,310 --> 00:27:52,850
Stop it!

454
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:55,810
Doing such a despicable thing at your age!

455
00:27:55,900 --> 00:27:57,160
Shameless!

456
00:27:58,930 --> 00:28:00,330
Are you going to explain?

457
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:03,440
Will they believe you if you explain?

458
00:28:07,700 --> 00:28:10,310
No one can even understand
your good intentions,

459
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:12,690
let alone believe anything else you say.

460
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:15,730
Zhang Hailou and your mentor are the same.

461
00:28:25,660 --> 00:28:29,400
[No animals were hurt
during the shooting]

462
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,630
Give me the cat!

463
00:28:41,660 --> 00:28:42,700
Let me go! You...

464
00:28:43,350 --> 00:28:44,460
Let go! You're hurting me!

465
00:28:44,460 --> 00:28:47,320
-Let go of my mother!
-Yuanbao! Come back! Yuanbao!

466
00:28:47,590 --> 00:28:48,390
Let me go!

467
00:28:48,550 --> 00:28:49,780
You're hurting me!

468
00:28:52,850 --> 00:28:53,660
No!

469
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:55,810
Let go of my mother!

470
00:28:59,810 --> 00:29:01,060
Give me the cat!

471
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:01,980
Let's go!

472
00:29:01,980 --> 00:29:03,330
Let's go home! Hurry!

473
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:23,270
I...

474
00:29:34,810 --> 00:29:35,480
Young Master,

475
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:37,440
you're awake? Breakfast is ready.

476
00:30:30,970 --> 00:30:33,190
[Murder]

477
00:30:33,290 --> 00:30:35,950
[Crossword Puzzle]

478
00:30:40,290 --> 00:30:41,150
[Murder]

479
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:47,680
[Murder]

480
00:30:49,460 --> 00:30:55,390
[Murder]

481
00:31:05,090 --> 00:31:06,550
Young Master, the doctor is here.

482
00:31:06,550 --> 00:31:08,350
He is waiting for you in the room.

483
00:31:14,050 --> 00:31:14,850
Young Master?

484
00:31:16,900 --> 00:31:17,830
