485
00:31:18,900 --> 00:31:19,700
I'm coming.

486
00:31:26,590 --> 00:31:27,980
Great. Yes.

487
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,290
Take a step. Come on.

488
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:30,360
Be careful.

489
00:31:31,740 --> 00:31:32,430
Be careful.

490
00:31:33,010 --> 00:31:34,050
Yes, very good.

491
00:31:34,850 --> 00:31:35,240
Yes.

492
00:31:35,940 --> 00:31:36,400
Come on.

493
00:31:36,850 --> 00:31:37,510
A little more.

494
00:31:37,510 --> 00:31:37,980
Yes.

495
00:31:40,640 --> 00:31:41,370
Are you okay?

496
00:31:43,550 --> 00:31:44,090
Steady.

497
00:31:45,550 --> 00:31:46,010
Come on.

498
00:32:03,850 --> 00:32:04,310
Come on.

499
00:32:05,810 --> 00:32:06,270
Good.

500
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:07,690
You can do it.

501
00:32:13,770 --> 00:32:14,630
Yes, very good.

502
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:15,340
Come on.

503
00:32:15,510 --> 00:32:16,110
Slow down.

504
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,420
Be careful. Steady.

505
00:32:23,590 --> 00:32:24,270
Hold on.

506
00:32:24,330 --> 00:32:25,680
Good. Keep your balance.

507
00:32:25,680 --> 00:32:26,140
Come on.

508
00:32:26,510 --> 00:32:26,980
Come on.

509
00:32:27,310 --> 00:32:28,440
You're doing great.

510
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:29,460
Come on.

511
00:32:29,850 --> 00:32:30,450
Good.

512
00:32:32,910 --> 00:32:33,440
Good.

513
00:32:36,670 --> 00:32:37,500
No rush.

514
00:32:38,180 --> 00:32:39,610
You were being awesome today.

515
00:32:39,610 --> 00:32:41,870
Let's stop here. I'll get you some water.

516
00:32:46,010 --> 00:32:47,100
Run!

517
00:32:52,220 --> 00:32:52,900
Slow down!

518
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:53,890
We're taking off!
